Triton Consolidated Companies 

 

Management:
The combined management team of Triton has been involved in the manufacturing and selling of various fabricated and manufactured products for many years.  Products include industrial equipment, elevators, elevator cab, aviation, industrial/commercial accessories and software. The management team is comprised of seasoned veterans in their respective industries and bring the strength of knowledge to cooperation that will help the Company reach its goals.
Markets:
Elevator – Triton services the residential and accessories segment of the elevator industry, including, low rise and limited use lifts and elevators and elevator cabs.
Fabrication – Triton provides specialty products to the industrial, commercial, residential and restaurant markets with stainless steel and polyethylene products including tanks, kitchens, building lobbies and other customers who need utility solutions.
Aviation Ground Support Equipment – Triton serves this market segment which is experiencing a vacuum of products and manufacturers while the aviation infrastructure is experiencing an ever increasing demand from the growth of the air transportation industry.
Technology – Triton Applied Systems with its software and services will target both the corporate integration market and the emerging “millennial” trending markets.  According to “Business Wire” the global System Integration Market will reach a value of $377.59 billion by 2020. Triton Applied will develop and deploy products and services into this market.
 
 













 

